      "title": "India hands over second aid consignment",
      "body_lines": [
        "The second consignment of aid from India with the assistance of the State Government of Tamil Nadu was officially handed over by the Indian High Commissioner to Sri Lanka Gopal Bhagle to the Minister of Health Dr. Keheliya Rambukwella today (24).",
        "It is said that the value of this stock of aid is over 3 billion Sri Lankan rupees.",
        "The 1,500 metric tonnes consignment includes 14,712 metric tonnes of rice, 250 metric tonnes of milk powder and 38 tonnes of essential medicines, Indian media reported."
